 Ability to handle large amount of data.
■ 處理離散型數學的能力
 Ability to do mathematics relating to discrete models.
□ 獨立研究與撰寫論文的能力
 Ability to do independent researches and to write thesis.
□ 使用計算機的能力
 Abilities to use computer as a tool.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       群同構定理，群作用，西羅定理，阿貝爾群基本定理，若爾當-赫爾德定理，p-群，冪零群，可解群。Basic concepts, the isomorphism theorems for groups, group actions, Sylow theorems, fundamental theorem of abelian groups, Jordan-Holder theorem, p-groups, nilpotent and solvable groups.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
解代中群與環的基本性質。深入討論群與環的結構。提供數學研究的代數方法。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Basic concepts and examples of groups,2Homomorphisms, normality and quotient groups, 3Isomorphism theorems for groups, Structure of cyclic groups4Group actions on sets, cosets and counting5Group actions on sets, cosets and counting6Symmetric, alternating and dihedral groups7Symmetric, alternating and dihedral groups8Free groups, generators and relations9Exam10Fundamental theorem of finitely generated abelian groups11Fundamental theorem of finitely generated abelian groups12Group actions on sets and their applications13Sylow Theorems14Basic concepts of rings and homomorphisms, examples15Ideal and quotients, Chinese remainder theorem.16Chinese remainder theorem, polynomial rings17polynomial rings, formal power series rings18Exam 

